sagex.phoenix.metadata.proxy

Interface IPropertyListFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CastMemberPropertyListFactory, GenrePropertyListFactory, MediaArtPropertyListFactory, StringPropertyListFactory

    public interface IPropertyListFactory
    Used to convert lists to strings and vice verse for specific types. Used in the property serialization and deserialize for sage metadata. A ListFactory implementation should accept the SageProperty in the constructor that it can have access to the current property if needed.
